short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: op Bulk QR Code Barcode Generator can generate ten thousands qrcode and print it online

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Bulk QR Code Generator makes QR Code generation really easy and fast. You just need to input an excel file and you can create thousands of QR Codes with just one click.
Features:
 Bulk QR Code Generator generates ten thousands QR Codes and more with very high performance. You can export all QR Codes to html file and CSV file
